name: MiniHaiku
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mini haiku
des: Mini Haiku provides you with a handful of enjoyable haikus about the change of seasons. Simply ask Mini Haiku to read you a haiku or poem and be delighted! The haikus are provided in random order each time you ask to hear a haiku.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
